{"tid":411296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國新歌聲來台  台大學生發起反＜中國新聲音＞行動","createTime":"2017-09-23T16:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T11:42:00.000Z","uid":37554,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ced2b0ed5769b3f18b69f7957d847cd7e5bc07b","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"中國浙江電視台選秀節目「中國新歌聲」24日在台大田徑場舉辦演唱會，北市文化局官網標榜是台北．上海雙城論壇的後續交流活動。但才搭舞台，就把台大花近4000萬元修繕的國際認證田徑場損壞。作家溫朗東今天在臉書上表示，「中國新歌聲」把台大田徑場弄壞，並被上海市台辦主任列入統戰政績，總括來說，是柯文哲延續了郝龍斌的中國交流政策，但是隨著台灣跟中國的關係變化，「這顆接來的球變得有點燙，快要把手燙傷啦！」 <br />\n<br />\n溫朗東說，「中國新歌聲」是個歌唱選秀節目，最近準備要開播第二季，看到幾個導師的名字（陳奕迅、那英、劉歡、周杰倫）就知道節目規格蠻猛的。嚴格來說，「中國新歌聲」並不是第二季，因為它是延續了「中國好聲音」，只是因為版權問題，名字改了。這節目跑去台大田徑場辦活動，是因為「台北上海城市論壇」中簽了一些合作備忘錄，這活動<br />\n是其中的一部分。"},{"pid":"0d22fa9c13969cb0ce6e4707541b8676bc9c0e69","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:23:31.000Z","msg":"溫朗東說，比較明顯的是「中國好聲音」時期，台灣人去參加，就算自己沒說，有時也會被加上來自「中國台灣」的字幕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/270400823453773/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F270400823453773%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=wEpdz9VwhN%2Bl139cOmf2NgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=cdcb4a03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/270400823453773/?fref=ts</a>"},{"pid":"495402104d2f874d894954406a17ad47b62fac4c","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"本次行動的目的是干擾、妨礙＜中國新聲音＞台大音樂會的進行。<br />\n<br />\n1. 將群眾聚集在操場場外，堵塞入場通道，干擾觀眾入場並拖延活動時程。<br />\n<br />\n2. 場外人數聚集足夠時，進入操場開始執行抗議。"},{"pid":"f0aa40a2a6b23d14f7a7a1c48b75a2fae2c4630a","tid":411296,"uid":50801,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作家溫朗東今天在臉書上表示，「中國新歌聲」把台大田徑場弄壞，並被上海市台辦主任列入統戰政績</blockquote><br />\n即係整爛運動場當做政績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1be13517d149ed626ed1874c5a760100aab55a4","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NTUSA/posts/1620460397975122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNTUSA%2Fposts%2F1620460397975122&d=wEpdz9VwhN%2Bl139cOmf2NgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=f26cbe49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NTUSA/posts/1620460397975122</a>"},{"pid":"189ca5eace4e5d52dec000e5756de8fae9ad710a","tid":411296,"uid":25900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"Taiwan NUMBER 1！！！！！！"},{"pid":"0f98f1a587b726880c875db63b949f2c06841b53","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"學生集合<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eXIGTL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeXIGTL1.jpg&h=5277ee1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fa3e8c27bd2af06eeecb640a79d6c63e1335eb7","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NTUcpaper/videos/10155630272420030/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNTUcpaper%2Fvideos%2F10155630272420030%2F&d=wEpdz9VwhN%2Bl139cOmf2NgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=a536a3fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NTUcpaper/videos/10155630272420030/</a>直播"},{"pid":"561ed297c6a88dfd2d9fae94e1b21edf79dfce3f","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LJdfxv0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLJdfxv0.jpg&h=0646599b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a51f5b6750b5a9ec1de96e83b0f0a27009da4aaa","tid":411296,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"成篇嘢都冇講反乜嘢？"},{"pid":"83e9ae1b6b4e14d17bd76b2eed7b1c0a5a5cf5c0","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"愛中國同心會<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iMu65sP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiMu65sP.jpg&h=2cc95c25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"868d897e965497d0ea46701c6f74313f498789b6","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"行動聲明稿: <br />\n我們是一群自發來到現場，對於由台北市文化局以「中國新歌聲－－上海．台北音樂節」名義協辦之「中國好聲音」節目借用台大田徑場一事，透過行動表達自身訴求的台大學生。確實，作為由不同成員自發組成的行動，彼此之間對此事件有不同的解讀，有部分同學著重於校方罔顧學生權益或校方場地租借程序上的黑箱，也有同學認為作為協辦單位的台北市府以非主辦的藉口試圖將責任推卸於台大校方，亦有同學主張此為中國透過文化活動名義對台灣進行統戰。但無論從何種觀點解讀本次活動，我們的共識皆認為這是一場應立刻停止舉辦的活動。<br />\n<br />\n1.台大學生會已在週五（9/22）對此事代表台大學生發表意見，我們也贊同學生會的三點訴求。但不同於學生會偏向事後監督與呼籲性質的訴求，作為台大構成主體的學生，對於此事件造成的不良影響，我們認為應更積極以個人身份表達對此事件的抗議，應採取比學生會更為積極與多元的主張。除了透過今天的行動，表現出不同學生對此事的不同觀點與訴求，也希望此事件得到足夠的關注，避免在活動結束後，此事件只淪為一時的話題，而未見任何實質上的改革與賠償。<br />\n<br />\n2.在程序面上，學生會主張校方應完整公布與台北市文化局、主辦單位申請過程，並說明為何早在八月時就通過的簽文，卻從未告知作為台大教學主體的師生。此外，學生會也訴求校方應該重新審議大型活動場地租借行政流程，避免重蹈覆轍，破壞校園體育環境。對此，我們認為學生會的訴求僅是偏重事後檢討與資訊公開的最低程度要求，台大校方不應僅是達成此最低程度的訴求為已足，對於此種嚴重影響學生權益卻完全欠缺正當程序的活動，我們認為應立刻停止舉辦並更換活動場地，一切財務上之損失與相關行政責任應由主辦與協辦單位自行承擔。<br />\n<br />\n3.除了程序上的瑕疵外，更應關注的實質的面向。我們認為縱然台大校方與主辦、協辦單位踐行合法且正當的程序，從實質上來看，本次活動也同樣不應在台大舉辦。換言之，不同於「立刻改進施工」的學生會訴求，我們認為應立刻停止在台大舉辦此活動。此刻並非寒暑假期，而是師生教學活動及社團活動對於場地使用有高度需求的時刻，一場對於場地維護產生高度風險且與教學活動、社團活動無關的私人活動，完全漠視田徑場設施設置的目的，也欠缺犧牲學生權益優先舉辦此活動的任何正當理由與優越利益。台大田徑場使用的優先目的應當是校內師生的教育與活動，甚至是提供周邊居民運動與休憩的空間，而非校方獲取（與維修費用）不合比例的低收益，或幫助台北市政府與中國政府間建立良好的政治關係。<br />\n<br />\n可能會有人批評我們是學生，應當好好念書，而非搞政治跟抗議鬧事。也可能有人會對於提出政治性訴求的同學加以批判，認為應該「音樂歸音樂，政治歸政治」。但請注意這是一場由「台北市政府文化局」協辦的活動，一場透過文化活動的形式進行台北市政府與中國方面合作的活動。換言之，這場活動本身就是高度政治性的，當政治活動進入台大校園，我們認為學生採取運動的手段或提出政治相關訴求表達對這場活動的抗議，是作為此校園主體的學生們應採取的合理行動，歡迎更多同學與市民朋友們加入我們的行列，挺身而出捍衛您的權益！"},{"pid":"eb6fcf5a21a51c07fdfa553146b2821982f076ad","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p480x480/21761974_1560553230633512_1487445109813859813_n.jpg?oh=ddc93579bedc07ce44b3e40af51c3d1b&amp;oe=5A4B2A85\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp480x480%2F21761974_1560553230633512_1487445109813859813_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dddc93579bedc07ce44b3e40af51c3d1b%26oe%3D5A4B2A85&h=aa08d93a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f848f20946ce64547e84114c19b8f2a17f944099","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/prveNIk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FprveNIk.jpg&h=36f04438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台大舉行「中國新聲音」節目，二十多名舉台灣國旗幟欲闖入會場，與阻擋人員發生推擠。<br />\n<br />\n台大學生今天在校內田徑場外抗議校方將田徑場租借給中國大陸選秀節目舉辦音樂會，造成跑道受損，更嚴重影響學生受教權。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸選秀節目「中國新歌聲」今天在國立台灣大學舉辦「2017『中國新歌聲』上海．台北音樂節」活動。有學生在場外繫上白布條抗議。<br />\n<br />\n上海市政府台灣事務辦公室主任李文輝今天也以上海市海峽兩岸交流促進會名譽會長身分出席活動，但低調不願受訪。<br />\n<br />\n發起抗議的蔡姓台大學生表示，由於演唱會工程關係導致操場跑道龜裂，無法使用，且操場封閉一週，所有涉及大操場的體育課程全部無法進行。<br />\n<br />\n他批評，台大為了區區新台幣65萬元租借費用，犧牲學生受教權與場地使用權，是「台大之恥」。<br />\n<br />\n在學生受訪同時，也有反對學生立場的民眾在一旁高呼「中國加油」、「日本人滾出去」等話語。"},{"pid":"a03f01af399d53fd3252e2982c8d84bbf6c796c3","tid":411296,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"台仔好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75746441e560ac0052f43869fac89c500e75401a","tid":411296,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6dddb6267073c3afeec16fbedb77032a67e9bb8","tid":411296,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣野<br />\n<br />\n大陸將「國立臺灣大學」<br />\n<br />\n寫左做「臺北市臺灣大學」<br />\n<br />\n臺大已經係臺大第一學府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2190ead880f8271d7fb06ffe95c3f7251fddc5","tid":411296,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一樣野<br />\n<br />\n大陸將「國立臺灣大學」<br />\n<br />\n寫左做「臺北市臺灣大學」<br />\n<br />\n臺大已經係臺北第一學府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"08c9fa2a6d44c0ba0957552d1e389ad0611a5507","tid":411296,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdda0ba2a0afffa6de74c9865a4f46cf300c600e","tid":411296,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5c9497a9b11089e6934474516ee136c98e0ad0","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"台大生抗議出借場地辦「中國」音樂節 校方因混亂終止演出"},{"pid":"0638390b04550cf480c9da781b176a82f85fcd1b","tid":411296,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"60303f359a6bcba6062b3f23c5a25dde1285a60a","tid":411296,"uid":90704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"搵件奶共妹，上節目大大隻字中國台灣<br />\n再出盡力數落自唔認識大陸<br />\n第一次返大陸好震驚發展成果<br />\n用認罪片手法玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd07d5b49ad6922e9568b2df319f5f5ed08d642","tid":411296,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"執行抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a2fb2ef63920d33ae9b3caf636f0e28956e170","tid":411296,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:28:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1681680485/videos/10208954132765505/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1681680485%2Fvideos%2F10208954132765505%2F&d=wEpdz9VwhN%2Bl139cOmf2NgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=208ba2b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1681680485/videos/10208954132765505/</a><br />\n愛國同心會 打人影片"}]}